    "description_long": "This is a bright red two-door sports car with a sleek, aerodynamic body and a low, aggressive stance. The hood and roof are finished in matte black, contrasting sharply with the glossy red bodywork. Chrome five-spoke alloy wheels and low-profile tires emphasize its performance-oriented design. The car features a prominent rear spoiler, dual exhausts, and tinted windows, suggesting high speed and power. The front end is characterized by a wide grille and a hood scoop, while the rear displays a continuous taillight bar. The overall appearance is modern, muscular, and built for urban or highway driving.",
